CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 2, 1946, pg. 19 reads: "Birthday Celebration - William Allen Dorsey, son of Corp. and Mrs.William Dorsey, celebrated his second birthday last Wednesday with a party at the home of his grandparents of 2307 Mahon Street. Guests included, left to right, front row: Joyce Barnett, Clyde Barnett, Mary Ann Scott, William Dorsey, Bernice Barnett, Blanche Scott; back row: Wilma Hart, Johnnie Buckner, Jacqueline Buckner, Alice Scott and Yvonne Buckner.  Lois Dorsey, not shown in photo, was also a guest. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of birthday party, from left, front row: Joyce Barnett, Clyde Barnett, Mary Ann Scott, William Dorsey, standing behind his birthday cake; Bernice Barnett, and Blanche Scott; back row: Wilma Hart, Johnnie Buckner, Jacqueline Buckner, Alice Scott, and Yvonne Buckner, posed behind table in home of William Dorsey's grandparents, 2307 Mahon Street
